metadata.name: Martian Bartender Cocktail #2
metadata.description: Cocktail NFTs that are out of this world.  Martian Bartender has crashed and needs your help to get off world.  He is willing to exchange his cocktails for some help and in return, Martian Bartender, will bring AR and WEB3 to your favorite restaurants and bars.  5,555 Unique tokens that grant holders access to special perks, early access to MARTIAN DROP and upcoming AR EXPERIENCES.  Custom Frames, Backgrounds, Planets, and Cocktails.  Everyone has a favorite drink.  What's yours? Please Drink Responsibly.
